\c 134 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 134\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyoon Jajachuutti Wal Waamuu (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an)
\m \bd 1\bd* Amma isin hojjetoonni Waaqayyoo hundinuu, warri halkan mana Waaqayyoo keessa dhaabattan, kottaa Waaqayyoon ulfinaan jajadhaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Gara iddoo qulqullaa'aa sanatti harka keessan ol kaasaa, Waaqayyoon ulfinaan jajadhaa!
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo inni waaqaa fi lafa uume, Xiyoon keessaa si haa eebbisu!
\b 
